(493, 'widget_ctup-ads-widget', 'a:6:{i:1;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:7:\"Apitiny\";s:4:\"text\";s:268:\"The app links everyone to events around them. You can create event, join and share event to your friend directly or through social netwoking. \r\n<br>Easily write a comment, review or make a conversation with others.\r\n<br>Apitiny has now arrived on Web, Android and iOS.\";s:4:\"link\";s:19:\"https://apitiny.com\";s:9:\"image_uri\";s:79:\"http://localhost/nguyenhiepsoftware/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/apitiny-logo.jpg\";s:15:\"custom_media_id\";s:1:\"5\";s:19:\"image_in_customizer\";s:87:\"http://localhost/nguyenhiepsoftware/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/apitiny-logo-150x150.jpg\";}i:2;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Race That Way\";s:4:\"text\";s:217:\"Race That Way is the most online racing game with features that bring you to the new world of racing. You will see it when playing the game.\r\n<br>\r\nThe game offers in-app purchase to buy cars and roads at high levels.\";s:4:\"link\";s:77:\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.thesimplestudio.racethatway\";s:9:\"image_uri\";s:78:\"http://localhost/nguyenhiepsoftware/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/racethatway.jpg\";s:15:\"custom_media_id\";s:4:\"9559\";s:19:\"image_in_customizer\";s:86:\"http://localhost/nguyenhiepsoftware/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/racethatway-150x150.jpg\";}i:3;a:6:{s:5:\"title\";s:15:\"English Spanish\";s:4:\"text\";s:203:\"More than 50,000 people around the world using English Spanish app every day for their daily conversation. \r\n<br>\r\nThe app comes to the world to leverage both your English and Spanish with cool features.\";s:4:\"link\";s:74:\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/english-spanish-in-use-voice/id789660618?mt=8\";s:9:\"image_uri\";s:72:\"http://localhost/nguyenhiepsoftware/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/spain.jpg\";s:15:\"custom_media_id\";s:4:\"9554\";s:19:\"image_in_customizer\";s:80:\"http://localhost/nguyenhiepsoftware/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/spain-150x150.jpg\";}i:4;a:6:{s:5:\"title\